=====Usage notes=====
The surnames {{l-self|zh|肖}} and {{zh-l|蕭}} were originally distinct, and {{l-self|zh|肖}} was a rare surname. In Mainland China, {{zh-l|蕭|tr=-}} was simplified to {{l-self|zh|肖}} in the {{w|second round of Chinese character simplification}} promulgated in 1977. Though the second round of simplification was officially rescinded in 1986, many individuals in Mainland China originally surnamed {{zh-l|^蕭}} but had their surname simplified to {{l-self|zh|肖}} did not change their surname back to {{zh-l|^蕭}}. Most individuals who bear the surname {{zh-l|肖|tr=Xiāo}} now were in fact originally surnamed {{zh-l|^蕭}} or descended from individuals originally surnamed {{zh-l|^蕭}}.

